comments.body:
nit: we require exactly one child, so I think using `tx_parent` is unnecessarily confusing
```suggestion
        BOOST_CHECK(IsChildWithParents({tx_child}));
        BOOST_CHECK(IsChildWithParentsTree({tx_child}));
```

